# AeroStars UAV Telemetry and Navigation System

A lightweight, real-time telemetry and basic navigation system built using **Arduino Nano**, **NRF24L01**, **HC-05 Bluetooth**, and a custom **Android app**. Designed for fixed-wing or UAVs, this system enables in-flight monitoring of key flight metrics such as voltage, GPS location, signal strength, and more.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- ğŸ“¡ **Wireless Communication** via NRF24L01 (long-range)
- ğŸ“ **GPS Integration** using TinyGPS++ for real-time lat/lon tracking
- ğŸ”‹ **Battery Voltage Monitoring** with voltage divider
- ğŸ“¶ **RSSI/Signal Strength** tracking (simulated, customizable)
- ğŸ” **1-second update rate** for live feedback
- ğŸ“² **HC-05 Bluetooth Output** to Android phone
- ğŸ“± **Custom Android App** for real-time data viewing
- ğŸ”§ Compact, modular code with easy expansion for more sensors

