## ğŸ§  System Architecture
[ UAV Side - Arduino Nano ] |--> GPS (TinyGPS++) |--> Voltage Sensor (Analog) |--> NRF24L01 (TX) | [ Wireless Link ] â†“ [ GCS Side - Arduino Nano ] |--> NRF24L01 (RX) |--> HC-05 Bluetooth Module â†“ [ Android App via Bluetooth ]

